\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Understanding data formats\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 The system expects a specific structure to read your instances and validate your solutions.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

