\f3\fs30\fsmilli15210 instances/
\f0\fs28  folder)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 There is an example that shows you how an instance should be written:\
	General information\
		number_of_request number_timeseps number_zones\
	clients information:\
		index_of_client zone_pickup zone-drop off\
				\'85\
	distance matrices: \
	each matrix is a matrix of nb_zones * nb_zones for a time-step\
	\
